regime

155
00:06:06,919 --> 00:06:09,860
would like to ensure a more China-friendly
president

156
00:06:09,860 --> 00:06:12,300
takes the reins in 2020.

157
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:13,590
And earlier this year,

158
00:06:13,590 --> 00:06:16,070
